OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779106274
OL,3,CMatt Taylor confirmed as permanent
OL,4,CExeter City manager
OL,6,FExeter City have confirmed that Matt
OL,7,FTaylor, who had returned to the club
OL,8,Fas interim head coach, has been made
OL,9,Ftheir permanent manager.
OL,11,FIt marks an official return for Taylor
OL,12,Fwho managed the club between 2018 and
OL,13,F2022, winning promotion from League
OL,14,FTwo in his final year as boss.
OL,16,FIt'll be that division Taylor will be
OL,17,Ftaking charge in again, he was unable
OL,18,Fto prevent the Grecians from being
OL,19,Frelegated from League One after
OL,20,Freturning to St James Park in March.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
