FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779106274
OL,3,CMatt Taylor confirmed as permanent
OL,4,CExeter City manager
OL,6,FFans at the club's stadium and the
OL,7,Fplayers were in tears as they failed
OL,8,Fto stay in the division for another
OL,9,Fseason.
OL,11,FSpeaking on the appointment the club
OL,12,Fsaid it had informal discussions with
OL,13,Fa number of candidates for the role
OL,14,Fwith Matt eventually being selected as
OL,15,Fthe new boss.
OL,17,F"Coming back to Exeter reminded me
OL,18,Fjust how special this Club is," Taylor
OL,19,Fsaid of his appointment.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
