PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779106274
OL,3,CMatt Taylor confirmed as permanent
OL,4,CExeter City manager
OL,6,F"There's work to do, on and off the
OL,7,Fpitch, as the whole Club goes through
OL,8,Fsomething of a reset and I'm excited
OL,9,Fto be part of this.
OL,11,F"We know we will need to rely on the
OL,12,Fyoung players, ideally through the
OL,13,Facademy system and this is one area
OL,14,Fwhere I have a great deal of
OL,15,Fexperience.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
