PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779106274
OL,3,CMatt Taylor confirmed as permanent
OL,4,CExeter City manager
OL,6,F"I'm grateful to the supporters for
OL,7,Ftheir backing. Over the 20 years I
OL,8,Fhave been involved with the Club they
OL,9,Fhave time and again proved their
OL,10,Floyalty and commitment. We'll be
OL,11,Fworking to bring the younger players
OL,12,Fthrough, supported by more senior
OL,13,Fmembers of the squad.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
