OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779106274
OL,3,CMatt Taylor confirmed as permanent
OL,4,CExeter City manager
OL,6,F"We want to have more local players,
OL,7,Fplayers who have grown up in the area
OL,8,Fand truly reflect the fact they are
OL,9,F'one of our own'. We know our
OL,10,Fsupporters appreciate this aspect of
OL,11,Fthe Club and perhaps are prepared to
OL,12,Fbe more understanding and give them a
OL,13,Flittle more time."
OL,15,FDan Green and Kevin Nicholson will be
OL,16,Fassisting Taylor with first-team
OL,17,Foperations.
OL,26,@uD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
