FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779106274
OL,3,CMatt Taylor confirmed as permanent
OL,4,CExeter City manager
OL,6,FWilf Walsh, Chair of the Club, said:
OL,7,F"A number of criteria were set for the
OL,8,Fposition, particularly around our
OL,9,Fsupporter ownership model and the
OL,10,Fimportance of the need to bring young
OL,11,Fplayers through our Academy.
OL,13,F"After a thorough analysis of the
OL,14,Fskillsets of a shortlisted number of
OL,15,Fcandidates and several informal
OL,16,Fdiscussions, it was very clear that
OL,17,FMatt was the most suitable and
OL,18,Fqualified person for the job.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779106274
OL,3,CMatt Taylor confirmed as permanent
OL,4,CExeter City manager
OL,6,F"He understands every aspect of the
OL,7,FClub. He knows how to get promoted out
OL,8,Fof League Two and he is absolutely
OL,9,Fcommitted to the Academy and the model
OL,10,Fof developing young players which has
OL,11,Fbeen so successful for us in recent
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,F"Matt will be a big part of a complete
OL,15,Freset across the Club, which will see
OL,16,Fus very much returning to our ethos,
OL,17,Fprioritising financial sustainability
OL,18,Fand supporter ownership powered by our
OL,19,FAcademy talent."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
